text:
Elm 327 Ford OBD-adapter game in a box without any instructions.
This product has a manual switch (switch beetween MS-CAn and HS-CAN.
There is not any mark in the product to which direction I should switch that switch to get MS-CAN connection or HS-CAN connection. No information of that even in your homepage.
